🐍 Classic Snake Game in Python – Simple, Fun, and Fully Customizable!
Welcome to the Classic Snake Game built in Python using Pygame – a perfect project for learning game development, building retro-style games, or adding to your portfolio!

🚀 Features
Smooth and responsive controls

Dynamic scoring system

Customizable grid size and speed

Clean and modular Python code

Ready to run with zero setup hassle

🎯 Ideal For
Beginners learning Python or Pygame

Developers looking to extend or contribute to a simple game

Educators teaching game loops, logic, or collision detection
